    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《掷个骰子》是一款结合策略和运气的桌面类骰子游戏，带你进入一个充满变化、挑战和惊喜的世界。在一个8*6的构筑表格上，玩家通过投掷骰子、激活格子、触发道具组合，积累分数并力求在每一关中超越自己。每回合依据骰子的点数和位置，结合精心设计的道具和套装效果，发挥策略，以赢得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你认为合适的道具或箭头并调整其在构筑表格中的位置，让它们能够发挥最大的作用</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/e2ce78dc6473043ac26ed5e866de4c47.poster.avif?t=1741104445\" width=800 height=602 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/e2ce78dc6473043ac26ed5e866de4c47.webm?t=1741104445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/e2ce78dc6473043ac26ed5e866de4c47.mp4?t=1741104445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >集齐并激活套装，为你提供强大的增益</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/812c594f53ed08d7528a60cd2a7e44d3.poster.avif?t=1741104445\" width=320 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/812c594f53ed08d7528a60cd2a7e44d3.webm?t=1741104445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各式各样的骰子为你前进之路保驾护航</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/248bc773d240e985b2289e78f745e636.apng?t=1741104445\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/248bc773d240e985b2289e78f745e636.poster.avif?t=1741104445\" class=\"bb_img\" width=470 height=140 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每个回合随机生成的关卡难度，让前行充满惊险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/db1d4f8e7c5327f5434fef7e55416576.poster.avif?t=1741104445\" width=590 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/db1d4f8e7c5327f5434fef7e55416576.webm?t=1741104445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/db1d4f8e7c5327f5434fef7e55416576.mp4?t=1741104445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这里你能体验到</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >75个不同效果的道具，策略选择</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24个不同效果的箭头，辅助增益</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30个不同效果的骰子，提升上限</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每回合随机的关卡难度，惊险挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祝你好运！！！</p></li></ul>",
